Identification.LongTitle: United Nations Observer Mission in Uganda/Rwanda (UNOMUR) Medal Order

Provision.Text: His Excellency the Governor General in Council, on the recommendation of the Prime Minister, is pleased hereby

Provision.Label: (a)
Provision.Text: to authorize Canadians to accept and wear the United Nations Observer Mission in Uganda/Rwanda (UNOMUR) Medal in recognition of honourable service with the United Nations Observer Mission in Uganda/Rwanda; and

Provision.Label: (b)
Provision.Text: to direct that that Medal follow the United Nations Operation in Mozambique (UNOMOZ) Medal, preceding the United Nations Assistance Mission in Rwanda (UNAMIR) Medal, in the order of precedence in the Canadian Honours System.
